[1mContribute

We are looking for two things from you. Articles and other Contributions.
Articles must be in ASCII format and must be emailed to this address:

woa@trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk

putting 'Articles' in the subject line. You will be sent an automated
reply which includes the password you need to get access to the
Contributors disk on our website at

www.trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk/csd.htm

Other contributions can be games, tools, pics, anims, sounds (not music
mods) or anything else you can think of. Please send details of what
you want us to do with your contribution, for instance, do you want us
to put it on our disk or just review it? Send contributions to:

woa@trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk

and put 'Contribution' in the subject line. You will be sent an automated
reply which includes the password you need to download the Contributors
disk.

If you have any general queries about our Contribution system then
email them to 

nb@trogsoft.freeserve.co.uk

and put 'WOA' in the subject line.

